<br>
With this rule, all Some_Troublemaker_01 needs to do to lock out anyone from holding raids is to schedule it for several month to a year in the future.  Voila, no one else can book.<br>
<br>
Wording that WOULD have made sense would have been something like &quot;There will be ONE public event on the calendar in any month.&quot;  A grand total of 12 public raids yearly for all unguilded people, gee, yeah, they're monopolising the planes!!!<br>
<br>
Or if thats too frequent, maybe &quot;in any two month period&quot;, or &quot;in any three month period&quot;, though by that point you better be adding wording along the lines of &quot;There will be ONE public event per plane...&quot;.<br>
<br>
